<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4505954>
    dc:description "FIGURES 12–14. Mesoventral keel of Troglocharinus fadriquei sp. nov. (12), T. hustachei (13)—Cova del Gel, Llimiana—and T. ferreri pallaresi (14)—Avenc de l’Esquerda, La Palma de Cervelló—." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4505954/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4505970>
    dc:description "FIGURES 58–63. viii female urite of Troglocharinus sendrai sp. nov. (58), T. fadriquei sp. nov. (59), T. mengeli (60)—Coves Encantades de Toloriu—, T. mercedesi (61)—Bòfia de Sant Jaume—, T. vinyasi (62)—Avenc de l’Home Mort—and Speonomites velox (63)—Querant del riu Merlé, Vilanova de Meià—. Spermathecal complex of T. mercedesi: CE, spermaduct; E, spermatheca; LA, apical lobe; LBS, basal lobe; RM middle region; VIII, eight urite." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4505970/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4505972>
    dc:description "FIGURES 64–69. Metendosternite of Troglocharinus impellitierii (64)—Cova Palomera de Taús—, T. quadricollis (65)— Graller de Castellet de Tremp—, T. mengeli (66)—Coves Encantades de Toloriu—, and Speonomites velox (67)—Querant del riu Merlé, Vilanova de Meià—. Metatergal apparatus of Troglocharinus senenti (68)—Querant Gran de Paús, Vilanova de Meià—and T. mengeli (69)—Coves Encantades de Toloriu." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4505972/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4505956>
    dc:description "FIGURES 15–19. Aedeagus in lateral view of Troglocharinus sendrai sp. nov. (15), T. fadriquei sp. nov. (16), T. mengeli (17)—Coves Encantades de Toloriu—, T. mercedesi (18)—Bofia de Sant Jaume—and T. vinyasi (19)—Avenc de la Roca del Corb." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4505956/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4505964>
    dc:description "FIGURES 35–47. Apex of the lateral stylus of the aedeagus of Troglocharinus ferreri (35)—Avenc Gran del Sant Roc, Begues—, T. fonti (36)—Cova d’Ormini, Montanissell—, T. hustachei (37)—Cova del Gel, Llimiana—, T. impellitierii (38)—Cova Palomera, Taús—, T. senenti (39)—Querant Gran de Paús, Vilanova de Meià—, T. subilsi (40)—Grallera de Cambrils—, T. mengeli (41)—Coves Encantades de Toloriu—, T. sendrai sp. nov. (42), T. fadriquei sp. nov. (43), T. orcinus (44)—Cova Gran de la Febró, Montblanc—, Speonomites velox (45)—Querant del riu Merlé, Vilanova de Meià—, S. antemi (46)—Cova dels Porredons, Baén—and S. latrunculus (47)—Cova del Lladre, Santa Linya—. Membranous lamina in yellow." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4505964/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4505944>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Majority rule consensus tree of the analysis with Bayesian probabilities in BEAST. Numbers in nodes, posterior probability (BEAST) (if>0.5) / Maximum likelihood boostrap (RAxML) (if>50). Scale in million years B.P. See Table 1 for details of the locality of the specimens." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4505944/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4505962>
    dc:description "FIGURES 27–34. Endophallus and schematic ampliation of the middle region of Troglocharinus sendrai sp. nov. (27–28), T. fadriquei sp. nov. (29–30), T. mengeli (31–32)—Cabana d’en Garraba—and T. mercedesi—Bòfia de Sant Jaume—(33–34)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4505962/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4505968>
    dc:description "FIGURES 52–57. Spermatheca of Troglocharinus sendrai sp. nov. (52), T. fadriquei sp. nov. (53), T. mengeli (54)—Coves Encantades de Toloriu—, T. mercedesi (55)—Bòfia de Sant Jaume—, T. mercedesi (56)—Avenc del Xato—and T. vinyasi (57)—Avenc de l’Home Mort." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4505968/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4505966>
    dc:description "FIGURES 48–51. Spermathecal complex of Troglocharinus fadriquei sp. nov. (48), T. mengeli (49)—Coves Encantades de Toloriu—, T. mercedesi (50)—Avenc del Xato—and T. ferreri (51)—Avenc del Sant Roc de Begues." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4505966/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4505948>
    dc:description "FIGURES 3–4. Habitus of the holotypus of Troglocharinus sendrai sp. nov. (3) and T. fadriquei sp. nov. (4)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4505948/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

